    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271530/extras/26a6a483a95b495f61e61dd11018eb23.avif?t=1751368747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271530/extras_big/26a6a483a95b495f61e61dd11018eb23.avif?t=1751368747 width=800 height=353 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🍿 Pop the Corn: Kernel Clicker 🍿</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the tastiest clicker game around! Pop the Corn: Kernel Clicker is all about turning tiny kernels into a mountain of delicious, profitable popcorn, one satisfying pop at a time!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 <strong>Pop 'til you drop:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop kernels into the pan and watch the magic happen</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect your popped treasures for cold, hard cash</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your popping game to churn out popcorn faster than ever!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💰 Chase that golden dream:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embrace the endorphins when you hear the jingle of the rarer golden popcorn</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your hard-earned cash on shiny new pans</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch up your popping scenery with unlockable skies</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎵 Unwind and relax:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let the satisfying pop-pop-pop soothe your stress away!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a calm, pressure-free gaming experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for unwinding after a long day or during short breaks</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏅 Pop and achieve at your pace:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of in-game and Steam achievements to unlock!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself with a variety of popcorn-popping goals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No rush, no pressure - just <i>pure</i> popcorn fun at your own pace, accompanied by some soothing jazzy tunes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pop the Corn: Kernel Clicker is your cosy corner in the gaming world. It's a small, fun game that's always satisfying to play, whether you've got five minutes or five hours. Let the rhythmic popping and gentle gameplay wash away your worries, and why not grab a bag of Popcorn to munch on as you play, because you deserve it! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Take it easy, and get popping!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271530/extras/92490275205db0933d63761215c7ce23.poster.avif?t=1751368747\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271530/extras/92490275205db0933d63761215c7ce23.webm?t=1751368747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
